      <div class="portlet">
        <div class="portlet-header portlet-header-bordered">
          <h3 class="portlet-title">Alignment</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="portlet-body">
          <p>Change the horizontal alignment of your nav with <strong>flexbox utilities</strong>. By default, navs are left-aligned, but you can easily change them to center or right aligned.</p>

          <!-- BEGIN Grid -->
          <div class="d-grid">
            
            <!-- BEGIN Nav -->
            <ul class="nav justify-content-start">
              <li class="nav-item">
