        <div class="portlet-header portlet-header-bordered">
          <h3 class="portlet-title">Additional elements</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="portlet-body">
          <p>You can combine other elements such as <a href="{{ 'elements/base/badge.html' | url }}">badges</a>, icon or caret to separate nav items, we provide <code>.nav-prepend</code> and <code>.nav-append</code> for wrapping those elements.</p>

          <!-- BEGIN Nav -->
          <ul class="nav nav-pills">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">
                <span class="nav-content">Link</span>
                <div class="nav-append">
                  <i class="caret"></i>
                </div>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link active" href="#">
